    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://fanfanshen.github.io/courses/BigDataStorage/chapter1/images/1.1-4.png&#34; alt=&#34;1.1-4&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
